creator: Loylogic Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Etihad Guest Reward Card is a mobile wallet that allows you to convert your Etihad Guest Miles into cash and load them onto your Visa Reward Card for online and in-store shopping worldwide. You can convert your miles into cash instantly, easily and securely to spend them on whatever you want, wherever Visa cards are accepted.

With this award-winning loyalty app you can find your dream reward on Macy's or Gap, you can pay your bills or spend your miles at your local department store - the possibilities are endless!

Wishing you an amazing shopping experience!

Your Reward Card Team

For more information, please visit http://www.rewards.etihadguest.com/reward-card
